        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】Sony XYN 一站式 XR 解决方案，方便制作 3D 游戏、电影</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/10/sony-xyn/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-xyn</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/10/sony-xyn/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 09:00:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY XYN]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286302</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>CES2025 展会上，Sony 展示 3D 内容创作软硬件解决方案「XYN」，其中包含全新推出的 Sony XYN XR 头戴式装置、无需佩戴 3D 眼镜的专用荧幕及动作捕捉软件，专为创作者和专业人士设计，开启了创作和沉浸式体验的新篇章。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo051s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo051s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo051s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲头戴式装置，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WPBmlGIiAOE&amp;ab_channel=SonylXYN">Sony|XYN@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1286304 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125054-694x364.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125054-694x364.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125054.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲3D 物件捕捉功能</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo042s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo042s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo042s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲无须 3D 眼镜的专用荧幕，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WPBmlGIiAOE&amp;ab_channel=SonylXYN">Sony|XYN@YouTube</a></p><p>SONY XYN 采用 Android XR 平台，为用户提供前所未有的沉浸感和创作自由。XYN 头戴装置能够无缝切换到扩增现实（AR）模式，方便创作者在不同场景下都能高效运用。无论是制作 3D 模型、沉浸式影片制作，还是虚拟会议，SONY XYN 都能提供绝佳的视觉效果与互动体验。</p><p>Sony 官方新闻稿称，XYN 能够帮助创作者制作 3D 及 XR 电影及游戏，其可捕捉现实世界的物件、动作，并将其化为 3D 图像，于虚拟实境重现。SONY XYN 的显示技术，能够以极高的分辨率呈现出每个细节，无论是在细致的图像设计、游戏开发，还是电影制作过程中，都能展现出细腻的颜色和极为真实的画面质感。Sony XYN 还具备高效的运算处理能力，支援高效能的图形渲染，让创作者的每个构思都能在虚拟世界中精确呈现。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286305" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125259-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125259-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125259.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可捕捉 3D 物件</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286309" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010136-694x380.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="380" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010136-694x380.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010136.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲于专用荧幕重现物件</p><p>随著远程协作和混合工作模式的兴起，SONY XYN 为创作者提供了更高效的工具。这款个一站式解决方案在虚拟工作空间中为创作者提供更强大的协作支持，打破传统显示器和工作方式的限制。这款专为创作者设计解决方案，无论是在性能、沉浸感还是工作流程整合上，都展现出极高的水准。对于追求极致创作体验和高效工作流程的专业人士而言，SONY XYN 无疑是未来科技的重要象征。Sony 亦推出 XYN 专用荧幕，无须佩戴任何 3D 眼镜亦可即时阅览 3D 画面，更加可追踪用家头部显示 3D 内容，让用家有如亲历其境一样。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286313" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo043s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo043s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo043s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286307" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125557-694x389.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125557-694x389.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125557.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286306" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125418-694x388.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125418-694x388.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110125418.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲随著用家改变阅览角度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286308" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010140-694x374.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="374" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010140-694x374.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011010140.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲荧幕可相应显示 3D 物件不同角度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286311" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012211-694x388.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012211-694x388.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012211.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286312" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012201-694x388.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012201-694x388.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011012201.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo053s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo053s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo053s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286315" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo028s-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo028s-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xynlconceptvideo028s.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_69735"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WPBmlGIiAOE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://xyn.sony.net/en/">Sony</a>、unwire.hk</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
